N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 49.3 - Annuity certificates

State Regulations

The forms of annuity certificates issued or issued for delivery in this State by any fraternal benefit society transacting business under sections
4501 (l)
and
4505 (a)
of the Insurance Law, shall conform in all respects to section 3219. Notes
